      "content": "hey i'm looking at my mortgage statement from wells fargo and i'm kinda confused. i have a 30 year fixed at 6.5%. i want to know how the breakdown of my payment changes over time. like, can you explain how much of a typical payment goes to interest vs principal in the 5th year compared to the 25th year?",
