      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense, but can you actually show me the math? like, if my monthly payment is around $2,500, what would the rough split look like for a single month in year 5 versus a single month in year 25? i just want to see the actual numbers to make sure i'm understanding the scale of the difference.",
