    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's crazy how much of the money just disappears into interest at the start. it feels like i'm just paying for the privilege of having the loan instead of actually owning anything. is there anything i can do to stop that \"leakage\" or make more of my money actually hit the principal sooner?",
