      "content": "The best way to combat that initial interest \"leakage\" is by making extra payments directly toward the principal balance. Even sending a single extra payment or applying extra funds bi-weekly can drastically accelerate your payoff schedule. This extra cash flow will immediately reduce the principal, causing less interest to accrue in the following months. Essentially, you are pre-paying the interest expense!",
      "source": "target",
